{"id":292956,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/维权网-陕西省凤阳县刘强志北京爬高塔求见省委/","date":"2013-05-10T16:16:08Z","modified":"2013-05-10T16:16:08Z","title":"维权网 | 陕西省凤阳县刘强志北京爬高塔求见省委书记（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员田静民报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日早上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>点多</span><span>钟，陕西省凤阳县官塘镇的刘强志，爬上位于北京南站长途汽车站东南</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span>米</span><span>处高达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">70</span><span>米</span><span>的电信塔要求见省委书记。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>中午，各地在京访民陆续聚集到现场。只见周围停靠多辆警车，但没有施救。现场有人打北京政府热线</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12345</span><span>，要求尽快施救……电信塔上的人到底是谁？什么地方的？谁都不知道，大家都焦急地等待着。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>维权访民找来一张大纸，写上现场一人的电话号码，大家一起向电信塔上的人喊话，终于知道了此人是陕西的刘强志及电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18712066055</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，刘强志因上访已经多次爬高塔抗议，并在第二次爬塔后被劳教一年，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20 </span><span>日劳教期满。因对问题解决不满同年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>又一次进京上访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>刘强带儿子到了北京正常上访，没有想到在北京的国家信访处儿子被抢走、自己被打，故于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>凌晨又爬上了信号塔，被带到北京永外派出所后治安拘留十天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 2012</span><span>年的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>刘强志被带回了凤阳县的派出所询问，最后以辱骂领导为由拘留十天，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 2012<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">年</span></span>12<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span></span>30<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日</span></span></span><span>被告知劳教</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>个月。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日</span><span>刘强志收到一份解除劳教的通知书。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘强志认为自己的问题始终没有得到合理解决，所以再一次爬电信塔要求见省委书记解决问题。直到发稿时刘强志仍在电信高塔上坚持着。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-02SJAVeOaaQ/UY0GMqPAq2I/AAAAAAAAhu4/fuKLdxbhISU/s1600/2013-05-10+16.40.05.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-02SJAVeOaaQ/UY0GMqPAq2I/AAAAAAAAhu4/fuKLdxbhISU/s320/2013-05-10+16.40.05.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Sy9x0uwQwJc/UY0GRlfJi-I/AAAAAAAAhvA/9Y7viimzg8s/s1600/2013-05-10+16.56.11.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Sy9x0uwQwJc/UY0GRlfJi-I/AAAAAAAAhvA/9Y7viimzg8s/s320/2013-05-10+16.56.11.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_iLa3A8zD_o/UY0GLOeoyKI/AAAAAAAAhuw/EgAsf0bBhmY/s1600/2013-05-10+15.59.23.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_iLa3A8zD_o/UY0GLOeoyKI/AAAAAAAAhuw/EgAsf0bBhmY/s320/2013-05-10+15.59.23.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <